<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Islamic World</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #006a4e;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .photo {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 350px;
            display: block;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #006a4e;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Islamic World</h1>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <h2>About Islam</h2>
    <p>
        Islam is a religion of peace. Muslims believe in one God (Allah) and follow the teachings of Prophet Muhammad (PBUH).
    </p>

    <img src="your-photo.jpg" class="photo" alt="Islamic photo">

    <h2>Important Beliefs</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Belief in One God</li>
        <li>Prophethood</li>
        <li>Holy Quran</li>
        <li>Day of Judgment</li>
        <li>Angels</li>
    </ul>
</div>

</body>
</html>
